title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-07-2013 MON
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show OCT-07-2013 MON



Monday, October 07, 2013










Federal Budget Process Explained!

 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. Mike deconstructs two letters to the editor. 2. A discussion of political division in the Congress.

 - 10AM hour

Money Monday with financial expert, Jordan Goodman.

 - 11AM hour

Mike explains the federal budget process with particular attention to the 

 1995 budget crisis when Bill Clinton closed down the govenment.
